title: I Will Become An Immortal
alternative_titles: A Record of a Mortal's Journey to Immortality
summary: I Will Become An Immortal The village boy Han Li was born poor. To subsidize households expenses,he joins the Qixuanmen Sect. Because of his spiritual roots, he was accepted as a disciple by the mysterious Doctor Mo and started to practice “Changchun Gong” arts under his mentorship. Although his qualifications are mediocre, Han Li embarked on the dangerous road of immortal cultivation with his unyielding will and a mysterious vial picked up by accident. A Record of a Mortal’s Journey to Immortality Mortal Cultivator 凡人修仙传
